 1. Add a monthly operator report that shows daily meters per operator, plan, and percentage.
 2. Add an attendance report (tabel) that shows who came to work each day of the month.

 We already have the backend endpoints for these:
   - GET /reports/monthly/excel -> returns Excel file for monthly operator report
   - GET /attendance/export -> returns Excel file for attendance (tabel)

 We will add two new report cards in the ReportsPanel for these.

